<div class="title">Beer Brewers and Home Growers Unite</div>
<div class="substance">Cannabis Cultivation</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=DTM&Exact=1">DTM</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; DTM. "Beer Brewers and Home Growers Unite: An Experience with Cannabis Cultivation (exp9134)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Aug 31, 2001. erowid.org/exp/9134</div>

